                <br>

                <h3 style="color: #ffffff; text-align: center">Coding = Creating</h3>
                <br>

                <p style="color: #ffffff">
                    Imagine the sense of accomplishment for your child when she creates her very first computer program.
                    At NextCodeNinja, we train kids in the art of software development, and they get a personalized
                    laptop, built in class to continue practicing their skills from home.
                </p>
                <br>

                <p style="color: #ffffff">
                    In software development, the greatest developers are sometimes lovingly referred to as NINJA. They
                    can create amazing pieces of software (you're reading these words on the software of some of those
                    ninjas). Our goal is to help make the world's Next Code Ninjas - we can't even imagine what kind of
                    amazing things they'll be able to create.
