                        <h2>3. Code Kit</h2>

                        <p>
                            Each Code Kit begins with an Acer Chromebook, pre-loaded with Linux and a <a
                                href="faqs.html#codekits">variety of programming languages</a>. We also include a manual
                            for getting started and working offline. Having a personal laptop greatly increases a
                            child's productivity while learning software development. These kits are $250 each, and
                            financial assistance is available. We don't want anyone to miss out on the opportunity to
                            learn software development due to financial constraints, so we are always seeking donations
                            to make sure every child has their very own laptop.
                        </p>
                    </div>
