                        <h2>4. Curriculum</h2>

                        <p>
                            During the first few classes, we will be setting up our new laptops for software
                            development. The children will be building their own software systems from the ground up.
                            Then, we will begin a course of study specifically designed for elementary school students.
                        </p>

